column5: While tendin to the neighbourhood stray cat population, this little guy is making repeat visits..
What a cute opposum, they LOVE cat food!  Pam
Clampet aint that dinner for gramma and jethro?  Gerritt.
Mmmmmm  possum soup and hog jawls. It's all yours Clampet - enjoy !  Hey Clampet - looks like you reached GUIDE status with this one.   Congratulations !
Put that crittey on a diet of cornbread and buttermilk for a couple weeks to fatten it up, and you got some fine eatin' there bubba!!!.. but you already knew that.
I agree with fattening him/her up because I can't see him/her at all.  Page can't be found!!!  Tom.
possum stew   hhhhmmmmmmm...yummy  cute little fella
cant see the pics....  i had a pet possum and it was just like a cat. walked around the house and did its duty in the litter box. too bad they have such a short lifespan
Their life span gets shorter the closer you are to the highway.
